OL,3,CMan arrested after woman dies
OL,4,Cfollowing collision in Birmingham
OL,6,FA man has been arrested after a woman
OL,7,Fhas died following a collision in
OL,8,FBirmingham.
OL,10,FPolice were called to Dartmouth
OL,11,FMiddleway just before 2:30am after a
OL,12,Fpedestrian was hit by a black Audi RS
OL,13,FQ8.
OL,15,FEmergency services tried to save the
OL,16,F28-year-old woman but she died from
OL,17,Fher injuries.
