OL,3,CMan arrested after woman dies
OL,4,Cfollowing collision in Birmingham
OL,6,FA 22-year-old man has been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of causing death by
OL,8,Fdangerous driving and driving whilst
OL,9,Funder the influence of drugs.
OL,11,FHe remains in custody for questioning.
OL,13,FPolice are appealing for witnesses or
OL,14,Fany drivers with dashcam footage to
OL,15,Fget in touch.
